messages.messageBody:
_____





Teen Gathering for *Unschoolers*

NY, NJ, CT and beyond

Meeting on Tuesday, March 18th, 3pm till 9:00pm

Come join group of unschooled teens for an evening to hang out.

**Bring a dish to share with the group for dinner. ** Bring items to donate
to local food pantry.**

We'll rent a movie or go out depending on movie choices.

(Parents are welcome to stay and socialize)

Hosted by Roxanne Gauchman (always unschooled) - Putnam Valley NY.

Please rsvp to rahrahski93@...


Spread the word to other *UNschooling* groups in CT, NJ and NY area.

Please feel free to forward this email to other unschooling lists or
unschooling teens you know.






_____
